    question: '<p>Which statement is true regarding the <code>&#x3C;dfn></code> element?</p>\n<p>???</p>\n<pre><code class="language-html">&#x3C;p>\n&#x3C;dfn>Enki&#x3C;/dfn>\nis an app providing daily workouts\nfor your dev skills.\n&#x3C;/p>\n</code></pre>\n',
    answers: [
